WEBVTT

NOTE
Silent screen capture — these captions describe the on-screen action.

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
[No audio] MetaProc opens in the browser — nothing to install.

00:06.000 --> 00:12.000
The pairwise binary-outcome (2×2) template loads a worked risk-ratio example and runs it.

00:12.000 --> 00:28.000
Results: pooled risk ratio 0.69 (95% CI 0.62 to 0.78) across 10 studies, I² = 0%.

00:28.000 --> 00:50.000
Scrolling the results: heterogeneity, the 95% prediction interval, and a clinical translation with NNT/NNH absolute effects.

00:50.000 --> 00:58.000
Appraise tab: the GRADE certainty form, with suggestions pre-filled from the live analysis.

00:58.000 --> 01:08.000
Report tab: choose sections, generate an HTML, PDF, or R Markdown report — or download the reproducibility bundle.

01:08.000 --> 01:13.400
Plots studio: the saved forest plot, re-drawn — with the exact R code that drew it shown beneath.
